name: [LoCon/LoRA] Octans/八分儀 Style
description:
This is a LoCon model trained from 150 images about galaxy&ruins background,the Milky Way reminds me of a long voyage,and that's where the name comes from.

You can use the locon to design night star,inverted reflection in water,don't forget flowers

Weight 1.0 will perform better.

Trained with multires noise, and it's a LoHa model.

Same trigger as ver 1.0
